title.Name: title
title.Value: Arkansas Track and Field Presents Common Errors and Corrections Men's Hurdles

description.Name: description
description.Value:
2012 USTFCCCA South Central Region Men's Assistant Coach of the Year, Doug Case, takes you through a teaching progression for one of the most physically demanding events in track & field; the hurdles. Using a simple, straight forward approach, Coach Case takes you through the drills and teaching points needed to learn  various hurdling events from start to finish.

For information on purchasing this DVD, go to: http://www.championshipproductions.com/cgi-bin/champ/p/Track-Field/Arkansas-Track-and-Field-Presents-Common-Errors-and-Corrections-Mens-Hurdles_TD-04249B.html?mv_source=youtube

For more information on additional Track & Field DVDs, go to:
http://www.championshipproductions.com/cgi-bin/champ/track-and-field-dvds-videos.html
